revisions.description: Published as RFC 2954. The major new features of this revision include: o Support for read-write capability to provision switch components providing service, o Support for cross-connection via a frame relay to ATM service interworking function, o Support for frame relay fragmentation, o Additional frame counters to track frame loss. Refer to Appendix A for a comprehensive list of changes since RFC 1604.
